LandmineType.name: Bombabom
LandmineType.description: A mid-duration landmine that does the lowest damage. Valued for its cheap production the Bombabom is a good landmine to have for those finishing kills.

LandmineType.name: BigBertha
LandmineType.description: Large warhead Landmine that does the largest damage. Careful though as it is unstable and has the shortest duration.

LandmineType.name: BunkerBlocker
LandmineType.description: Blocks Bunkers. This Landmine will last 24 hours which outlasts any shield dealing a unexpected blow when they wake up!

OtherType.name: LootDrop
OtherType.description: A Loot Drop. This will give you items, coins, rank points and health when you collect it! Reward is based on its rarity.

OtherType.name: Shield
OtherType.description: A standard Shield that will protect you from incoming missiles and landmines.

OtherType.name: LandmineSweep
OtherType.description: This can be used to show all landmines for 2 minutes. Use wisely!

OtherType.name: UltraShield
OtherType.description: The powerful shield that will protect you from all incoming attacks for a longer duration than the standard shield.

MissileType.name: Buzzard
MissileType.description: A fast paced low damage missile

MissileType.name: TheNuke
MissileType.description: The most powerful missile in the game

MissileType.name: Amplifier
MissileType.description: A powerful cost effective missile with small radius high damage effect.

MissileType.name: ShieldBreaker
MissileType.description: A shield destroyer capable of destroying shields.

MissileType.name: Ballista
MissileType.description: A powerful missile with a wide blast radius.

MissileType.name: GutShot
MissileType.description: A fast missile with a long fallout.

MissileType.name: ClusterBomb
MissileType.description: Fires a cluster of missiles down.

MissileType.name: CorporateRaider
MissileType.description: A fast missile like the Buzzard but deals higher damage.

MissileType.name: Zippy
MissileType.description: The fastest missile in the game.
